      "v15.4_new_tour_creation": "Created new tour from external reference product t1192332 (Busan-Gyeongju spring cherry blossom day tour). Structural template: busan-gyeongju-unesco-legacy-tour-national-museum (same Busan→Gyeongju logistics, shuttle small_group format). Content layered with cherry-blossom-specific POIs added to KB v1.1: bomun_lake, daereungwon_tomb_complex, cheomseongdae. POI operational data sourced from VisitKorea, Visit Busan, Gyeongju City tourism office, 시장 참고 자료 listings, KoreaTravelEasy, Seoul Pass listings (cross-verified across 4–6 sources per POI). SEASONALITY is STRICT: spring=1.0, summer/autumn/winter=0.0 — tour operates only Mar 28–Apr 10 (verified from external reference t1192332 dating and 시장 참고 자료 listings 2024–2026). MATCHING-PROFILE SCORING METHODOLOGY: All 68 fields scored from verified facts about the actual stops in the default itinerary (walking distances measured, accessibility per VisitKorea + AllTrails, hours/admission per official tourism boards, UNESCO designations per UNESCO World Heritage List). Inline reasoning for each non-trivial score is captured as comments in the generator script step3b_create_cherry_blossom_tour.py — Jason can review or adjust any specific score by editing the generator and re-running. Key derivations: (1) walking_level=0.50 from measured 3–5km total walking with mostly flat paths and one stair section; (2) unesco_fit=0.95 from 3-of-4 stops being UNESCO-listed; (3) seasonality.spring=1.0 + others=0.0 from verified seasonal-only operating dates; (4) couple_fit=0.95 vs young_kids_fit=0.50 from cherry blossom romance vs 8.5h day length tradeoff; (5) value_for_money_fit=0.85 from 4 free admissions + shuttle pricing in peak demand season. REASONABLE-ASSUMPTION FIELDS that may need patching once the live external reference page is reviewed: (a) price.amountLabel left empty (per-person pricing TBD); (b) catalog_card.priceFromUSD null; (c) exact pickup times (08:00/08:15/08:30) assumed from typical shuttle schedule; (d) reviewsSummary populated with zeros — actual external reference reviews not imported in this pass; (e) hero/og images deferred per v15 P3 image workflow.",
